---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
    title="Security Installation Blog"
    description="Latest articles and guides about security system installation, CCTV, alarms and access control systems in New Zealand.">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Security Installation Blog</h1>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <article class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/cctv-installation.jpg" alt="CCTV Installation" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">
                        <a href="/blog/cctv-installation-guide" class="hover:text-blue-600">Complete Guide to CCTV Installation</a>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Learn about the best practices for installing CCTV systems in your home or business, including camera placement and wiring considerations.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                        <span>June 15, 2023</span>
                        <span class="mx-2">•</span>
                        <span>10 min read</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/alarm-systems.jpg" alt="Alarm Systems" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">
                        <a href="/blog/choosing-alarm-system" class="hover:text-blue-600">How to Choose the Right Alarm System</a>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">A comprehensive comparison of different alarm systems available in NZ, helping you make an informed decision for your security needs.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                        <span>May 28, 2023</span>
                        <span class="mx-2">•</span>
                        <span>8 min read</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/access-control.jpg" alt="Access Control" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">
                        <a href="/blog/access-control-systems" class="hover:text-blue-600">Modern Access Control Solutions</a>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Explore the latest trends in access control systems, from biometric readers to smartphone-based solutions for commercial properties.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                        <span>May 10, 2023</span>
                        <span class="mx-2">•</span>
                        <span>12 min read</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                <img src="/images/security-maintenance.jpg" alt="Security Maintenance" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">
                        <a href="/blog/security-system-maintenance" class="hover:text-blue-600">Security System Maintenance Tips</a>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Essential maintenance tips to keep your security systems running efficiently and effectively throughout the year.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                        <span>April 22, 2023</span>
                        <span class="mx-2">•</span>
                        <span>6 min read</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
